60
00:04:31.854 --> 00:04:35.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-You see that, don't you?
-I believe he loved her.

61
00:04:36.276 --> 00:04:39.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He is capable of love.
That's the source of his conviction.

62
00:04:40.113 --> 00:04:41.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
If you love something,

63
00:04:41.698 --> 00:04:44.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
you act to keep it with you
for as long as you can.

64
00:04:45.660 --> 00:04:49.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Instead, he allowed her to be killed
by other humans.

65
00:04:49.789 --> 00:04:50.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He wasn't there.

66
