a loyal servant of the night world,

84
00:06:05.531 --> 00:06:08.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
a prized asset in our lives and wars,

85
00:06:09.452 --> 00:06:12.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
