-What?

86
00:06:13.456 --> 00:06:15.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're human, Hector.

87
00:06:17.752 --> 00:06:22.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You threw in your lot with us because
it was your path to greatness and joy.

88
00:06:23.841 --> 00:06:25.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But your loyalty counts for nothing

89
00:06:26.010 --> 00:06:28.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
when a man who has decreed death
to all humans,

90
