in mad fury.

92
00:06:35.103 --> 00:06:39.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I ask you again,
does that sound sane to you?

93
00:06:40.775 --> 00:06:42.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He promised me that this would be a cull.

94
00:06:43.152 --> 00:06:46.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
That humans would be reduced
in numbers and controlled.

95
00:06:47.365 --> 00:06:49.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He is Dracula, Hector.

96
00:06:50.284 --> 00:06:52.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why would he tell the truth to a human?

97
00:06:53.704 --> 00:06:54.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Even you?

98
00:06:55.873 --> 00:06:58.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[sighs]
