you will continue to do it.

101
00:07:08.761 --> 00:07:12.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You just have to answer
one question for me.

102
00:07:12.598 --> 00:07:13.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And what's that?

103
00:07:14.809 --> 00:07:18.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Are you prepared to abandon Dracula
to win the war?

104
00:07:21.315 --> 00:07:23.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You don't say something like that
out loud in this place.

105
00:07:24.694 --> 00:07:25.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What matters more?

106
00:07:26.070 --> 00:07:29.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Wiping the earth of the humans you hate
and submitting to your own death,

107
00:07:29.574 --> 00:07:32.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
