108
00:07:33.828 --> 00:07:36.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The Castle must land at Braila, Hector.

109
00:07:37.290 --> 00:07:39.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Why?
-Because I wish it.

110
00:07:41.210 --> 00:07:44.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
