So I know you are still my friend.

136
00:09:52.758 --> 00:09:56.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I was being hunted by brigand magicians
who wanted to kill me,

137
00:09:57.597 --> 00:10:00.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
cut me up and sell my parts
to other magicians.

138
00:10:01.892 --> 00:10:04.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Someone like me is, in parts of the world,

139
00:10:05.062 --> 00:10:08.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
a rich supply of ingredients for potions,

140
00:10:08.149 --> 00:10:11.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
