141
00:10:12.612 --> 00:10:15.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-And you saved me.
-I did.

142
00:10:16.657 --> 00:10:19.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The only person in the world
who ever lifted a hand

143
00:10:19.452 --> 00:10:20.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
to protect me from anything.

144
00:10:22.371 --> 00:10:23.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And he was not a human.

145
00:10:25.374 --> 00:10:27.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You are still my friend.

146
00:10:28.210 --> 00:10:29.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I am.

147
00:10:29.837 --> 00:10:31.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I do have need of your work.

148
